{"tid":1087407,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[自殺/欺凌] 跳下去的一秒 (動畫版）","createTime":"2019-04-01T10:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T07:51:16.000Z","uid":79912,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6ed20ac40c821a127bad38e0f84ee9ce2be929","tid":1087407,"uid":79912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFB5oz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFB5oz1.jpg&h=2bdac28f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n動畫連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ld_PIJCBLwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fld_PIJCBLwU&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=a8aeb609\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ld_PIJCBLwU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好~！其實我估都無人看，不過既然整左，即管貼響到睇下有無人睇啦～<br />\n<br />\n終於！第一套動畫 -《跳下去的一秒 ~Another Ending~》出爐了~！而且結局是和繪本不同的~！ 大家快D睇我的動畫啦！<br />\n<br />\n支持我的話，記得幫我網上訂購我的繪本了~<br />\n<a href=\"https://naloklok.com/shop/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnaloklok.com%2Fshop%2F&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=ade5db40\" target=\"_blank\">https://naloklok.com/shop/</a><br />\n<br />\n也可以subscribe我的Youtube Channel~<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FjaipG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FjaipG&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=ebbdd400\" target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2FjaipG</a><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n故事後記:<br />\n<br />\n香港有時候是一個很悲情的城市。<br />\n新聞曾報導過，平均每9.3日就有青年自殺。<br />\n<br />\n我這動畫短片，當然不能阻止這些事的發生。<br />\n<br />\n但我仍希望這短片能告訴大家：<br />\n有尋死念頭的人為何要尋死，想下我們可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n另外, 我亦想告訴有尋死念頭的人：<br />\n你看到或聽到的不一定是事實的全部；<br />\n而且，你的死甚至影響著你的親人和友人往後的人生。所以，在你想著要尋死的時候，請再冷靜點想清楚圍繞著你的所有人與事。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家看到底。"},{"pid":"dcd8081e9402b7cfaa2b33d20b85b4c8e233dcb6","tid":1087407,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾又靠連登搵錢<br />\n<br />\nReport你個垃圾channel"},{"pid":"b527048e36dd3ae8f11f23c9f5fca55c51bc4c67","tid":1087407,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"自殺都比你條撚樣消費去搵錢<br />\n<br />\n人渣"},{"pid":"a283ade46d8a8c4d180bcb13846f379f3f606daf","tid":1087407,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"想靠呢範搵錢為生？<br />\n<br />\n算鳩數吧啦你<br />\n<br />\n死去打份下賤工過一世啦<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔會餓死<br />\n<br />\n才能呢d野無得迫<br />\n<br />\n冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"080923b0394fa468d803f0d38abd43f53a9da0fa","tid":1087407,"uid":65858,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"上面個痴線佬做咩事3 combo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我特登睇曬成條片先留言 條片唔差呀 做咩咁激動"},{"pid":"969e3a3ac835ed754ff0a1f01117238714bfccc3","tid":1087407,"uid":79912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:10:20.000Z","msg":"其實聽完佢講，唔太開心。好地地花咁多時間整條片竟然比佢罵得體無完膚。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我話你知，我整得我就已經有覺悟有人唔鐘意睇。無論你點講，我得閒就會繼續畫落去，就係咁。"},{"pid":"f79ec44fa276abe082ce1d43680cb0351fcf1f90","tid":1087407,"uid":22959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"080923b0394fa468d803f0d38abd43f53a9da0fa","tid":1087407,"uid":65858,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"上面個痴線佬做咩事3 combo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我特登睇曬成條片先留言 條片唔差呀 做咩咁激動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"睇username"},{"pid":"124709e903ae0221c49b3fd1eab22c6abd0d4e34","tid":1087407,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"睇完都有小感動 依d悲劇真係每日都係香港發生緊<br />\n<br />\n樓上果個真係痴線佬黎 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eba01f0a45c7c72de25405902613577f879549b","tid":1087407,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy"